- jsonMultiOperationOptions: Json Array of MultiOperationOption. eg: "\[\{"operationType":"move","remotePath":"/README.md","destPath":"/folder1/"\},\{"operationType":"delete","remotePath":"/t3.txt"\}\]" return \{ "error":"", "result":"true", \}
